      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence study using at least three mesh refinement levels with GCI < 5% for primary QoI.",
      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed (2.1M, 5.8M, 14.3M elements). Richardson extrapolation and GCI analysis yield GCI < 2% for hemolysis index and wall shear stress. Achieved level exceeds MRL 2 requirement."
