      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions (flow rate, rotational speed, fluid properties) must match or bracket the simulated operating points.",
      "rationale": "In vitro experiments conducted at 5 flow-speed combinations (2–6 L/min, 2000–3500 RPM) matching CFD boundary conditions. Blood analog fluid (water-glycerol) properties verified against simulation inputs."
    },
    {
